query:
-- We want to extract the share of voice of each type of category segmentation for each type of event
SELECT 
	day
	, week_of_year(date(day)) AS week
	, CASE 
		WHEN day < '2018-10-04' THEN 'Before'
		WHEN day > '2018-12-31' THEN 'After'
		ELSE 'While' END AS time_period
	, partner_name
	, CASE
		WHEN product_banner = 1 THEN 'Pushed products'
		WHEN brand = 1 AND audience = 1 THEN 'Same Brand & Same Category'
		WHEN brand = 1 THEN 'Same Brand & Other Category'
		WHEN audience = 1 THEN 'Other Brand & Same Category'
		END AS segment
	, SUM(CASE WHEN event_name != 'Sales' THEN events ELSE 0 END) AS product_and_basket
	, SUM(CASE WHEN event_name = 'Sales' THEN events ELSE 0 END) AS onsite_sales

FROM
	-- Getting events by products anf joining with the differents product groups defined in the catalog
	(SELECT
		day
		, UPPER(prod.external_id) AS external_id
		, event_name
		, partner_id
		, COUNT(0) AS events
	FROM
		bi_data.partnerdb_bi_advertiser_event  CROSS JOIN UNNEST(products) AS prod
	WHERE 
		partner_id IN (1871, 1871, 1871, 1871)
	    AND partner_partition IN (871,871,871,871)
		AND date(day) BETWEEN date_add('day',-30,date('2018-10-04')) AND date_add('day', +30,date('2018-12-31'))
		AND event_name IN ('ItemPageView', 'Sales', 'Basket')
		AND site_type<>'instore'
		AND user_id IS NOT NULL
		AND user_id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
	GROUP BY 1,2,3,4
	) evt
	JOIN
		sfitoussi.comarket_catalog c ON c.partner_id = evt.partner_id AND c.external_id = evt.external_id
	JOIN bi_core.dim_partner dm ON dm.partner_id = evt.partner_id
	AND brand + product_banner + audience <> 0 
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4,5
